Package com.w10.risk_game.models.phases

Class PostLoadPhase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.w10.risk_game.models.Phase
      • com.w10.risk_game.models.phases.MapEditorPhase
        • com.w10.risk_game.models.phases.PostLoadPhase
  • public class PostLoadPhase
extends MapEditorPhase
    The PostLoadPhase class is a subclass of MapEditorPhase that represents the phase after loading a map in a game editor, allowing for editing and saving of the map.
    Author:
    Omnia Alam
